1
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:42,480
Lanqi Moyuan.

2
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:50,680
How dare you come back to Tiandao Palace!

3
00:00:51,400 --> 00:00:52,530
Why wouldn't I dare?

4
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,840
I see.

5
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:01,680
So you guys are in this together.

6
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:02,920
No.

7
00:01:03,040 --> 00:01:03,880
How could we be

8
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,239
in cahoots with a demon?

9
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:06,520
Speaking of accomplices,

10
00:01:06,520 --> 00:01:08,980
your Tiandao Palace is his real accomplice.

11
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:11,520
He suppressed the Nether Region for your Tiandao Palace.

12
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:13,400
Your Tiandao Palace gained both fame and fortune.

13
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:15,200
Then you kicked him to the curb when he was no longer useful.

14
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:17,130
What a great scheme you have going.

15
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:21,000
Lanqi Moyuan.

16
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:22,840
So you found someone

17
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,840
to stand up for you, huh?

18
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:26,920
I didn't expect

19
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:30,330
that a half-human, half-demon freak like you

20
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:32,890
would actually have someone speak up for you.

21
00:01:34,160 --> 00:01:35,360
My Tiandao Palace

22
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:36,759
only regrets not

23
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,259
finishing you off sooner.

24
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:39,680
Taishu Yi.

25
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:42,360
Not only did you keep the Likong Tribe in captivity for their blood,

26
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:44,039
but you also enslaved them for so many years.

27
00:01:44,039 --> 00:01:46,100
Do you still think you're justified?

28
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:54,200
Has the world become so indiscriminate between right and wrong?

29
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:01,400
If so,

30
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:04,720
there is no need for this world.

31
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:24,800
Source blood.

32
00:02:25,840 --> 00:02:27,560
Such pure source blood.

33
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:31,260
To think I left you stranded outside for over ten years.

34
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,000
Taishu Yi.

35
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:06,120
It seems you haven't recovered from the price you paid

36
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,850
to seal Lanqi Moyuan back then.

37
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,920
It seems heaven has destined our Wuji Sect

38
00:03:10,920 --> 00:03:12,160
to take the lead.

39
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,040
Oh no.

40
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,360
Don't let him get ahead of us.

41
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,160
Our Qingfeng Pavilion

42
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:17,160
must also take a share of the credit.

43
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:46,880
He is a human, yet he can use demonic energy?

44
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:48,000
Taishu Yi.

45
00:03:48,920 --> 00:03:49,480
It seems

46
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:52,840
the consequences of you sealing me back then are quite severe.

47
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,000
After so many years,

48
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,680
your cultivation

49
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,300
hasn't recovered either.

50
00:03:58,040 --> 00:04:00,080
In the back mountain of the Tiandao Palace,

51
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:02,540
you even opened up a rift to the netherworld,

52
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,040
using a human body

53
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:07,080
to draw in demonic energy to increase your cultivation.

54
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:07,720
However,

55
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,080
can a human like you

56
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:11,250
really use demonic energy?

57
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,060
Wuzhou.

58
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,460
Wuzhou.

59
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,640
Yuan.

60
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:48,740
You.

61
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,260
Come, take this medicine.

62
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,040
Lu Danyu.

63
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,800
Both of them are turning into demons.

64
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:55,880
If they are not stopped,

65
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,440
even if the world is not destroyed,

66
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:59,720
all living beings will suffer a catastrophic disaster.

67
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:00,120
Yuan.

68
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:01,600
Snap out of it.

69
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:02,520
Yuan.

70
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,570
Don't become a mindless demon.

71
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:33,260
If the source of the demonic energy is not resolved,

72
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,640
Taishu Yi cannot be defeated.

73
00:05:48,159 --> 00:05:49,080
It hurts.

74
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:51,240
Why doesn't it seem to be working?

75
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,520
Lu Danyu,

76
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,360
if you want to seal all the rifts to the Netherworld,

77
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:57,560
it will take at least half of your blood.

78
00:05:58,960 --> 00:05:59,760
It's fine.

79
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:01,080
I can hold on.

80
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:02,760
Yuan.

81
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:04,400
Squeeze out a little more.

82
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:05,260
Half of my blood

83
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,940
can seal the Netherworld.

84
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,120
I actually

85
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:41,880
lost.

86
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:47,640
Tiandao Palace really lost.

87
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:48,800
To think this behemoth

88
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:50,400
would actually fall one day.

89
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:55,140
Then the things in this palace...

90
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:57,780
naturally belong to whoever is fastest.

91
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:58,680
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

92
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,320
Don't let others beat us to it.

93
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:00,920
Go, go, go!

94
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,680
Brother Wuzhou.

95
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,040
The Likong Tribe.

96
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:15,360
They...

97
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:16,040
I know.

98
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:17,320
Leave it to me, Danyu.

99
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:19,090
Come,

100
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:19,560
Danyu.

101
00:08:22,440 --> 00:08:22,970
Xiaoxue,

102
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:23,960
let's go.

103
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:32,679
Grandpa.

104
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,600
I have finally

105
00:08:35,159 --> 00:08:36,320
avenged you.

106
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:38,799
Yuan.

107
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,770
I hope you can let go of the past from now on.

108
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,840
Live well for yourself.
